Abstrak: The article discusses abstract painting, and in particular the work of artists Raoul De Keyser, Joanne Greenbaum, and Rosy Keyser. Mary Heilmann is among artists who have taken inspiration from Greenbaum's work. Among Keyser's notable works are "After Joy Division," "The Ray," and "Heaven and Other Poems."
Sumber: Nation. 1/4/2010, Vol. 290 Issue 1, p34-36. 3p. 1 Color Photograph.
